model.name: Mitrophanov2016 - Extended Mitrophanov2011 Blood Coagulation Model (additional thrombin reactions)

body.p: Mathematical model of blood coagulation. Extended model of Mitrophanov2011 (which is an extension of Hockin2002). Additional reactions added involving thrombin. Modelling the effects of dilution and addition of recombinant factor VIIa, II, VII, IX, X, AT.
